lead_paragraph: Three of the men who were wrongly convicted in the brutal 1989 Central Park jogger attack said Friday that a $40 million settlement can't buy back the dignity or the time the case unjustly cost them.

headline.main: Men Exonerated in Central Park Jogger Case Speak
